1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:39,270
[1998]

3
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:39,920
Xiaolan,

4
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:42,120
I know you're upset.

5
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,840
But I lost my sister too.

6
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,500
It hasn't been easy for me either.

7
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:49,430
No matter what,

8
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,720
you still need to study hard.

9
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,690
As the teacher said,

10
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,560
since it's your first time
handing in a blank test paper,

11
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,759
they'll let it slide.

12
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:00,350
Don't do it again.

13
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,840
Okay?

14
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:30,450
[Composition title:
The Answer to Happiness]

15
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:34,570
[Episode 27]
[The Answer to Happiness]

16
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,360
I'm more concerned about is—

17
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:40,800
will we know each other at that point?

18
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,930
Will we be together?

19
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,240
Let me think.

20
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,560
Let me do the math.

21
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,630
Oh my god.

22
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,150
At that point,

23
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:52,590
you'll be an old man of 60,

24
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:54,910
and I'll only be 36,

25
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:56,090
in my prime.

26
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,680
I won't fall for you.

27
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,520
Alright.

28
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,710
I'm kidding.

29
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:06,030
I've confirmed it.

30
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,440
The original me isn't in this timeline.

31
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,070
And in that timeline,

32
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:13,430
the current you doesn't exist either.

33
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,800
So I cherish this,

34
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:17,110
and I really don't want to leave.

35
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,240
Alright.

36
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,090
Let's not talk about this.

37
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,120
Right now,

38
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:25,440
you're right in front of me,

39
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,740
and that's enough.

40
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:27,910
What if...

41
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,190
What if...

42
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:36,280
I'll find a way.

43
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,610
I'll definitely find you.

44
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,630
But...

45
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,710
you haven't seen

46
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,710
me in that world.

47
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,400
How would you know

48
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,190
if that's me?

49
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,490
As long as I see you,

50
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,210
I'll recognize you.

51
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,280
Just like

52
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,280
when we first met.

53
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,240
Fine.

54
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,870
When you see me then,

55
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,590
shout my name,

56
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,480
and I'll know who you are.

57
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,090
Xiaolan.

58
00:04:00,870 --> 00:04:01,400
Xiaolan.

59
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,840
Xia Xiaolan.

60
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:06,870
Xia Xiaolan!

61
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:10,190
Xia Xiaolan!

62
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,040
Okay, guys.

63
00:04:18,430 --> 00:04:19,390
She is the one,

64
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,950
the only one, Ji Ya.

65
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:24,270
My bride‑to‑be,
she's a famous fashion designer, guys.

66
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,390
Please meet her.

67
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:27,430
This is Patrick.

68
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:28,360
Ji Ya.

69
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:30,310
Wenxiu.

70
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:31,730
My best friend.

71
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:32,830
Hello.

72
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,630
That is...

73
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:35,430
my fiancé, George.

74
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,440
My best friend, Wenxiu.

75
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:38,400
G-George.

76
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,360
Yes, that's me.

77
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,430
That's so nice to meet you.

78
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:40,870
Hello.

79
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:42,750
Okay.

80
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:43,990
I will...

81
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,760
You can go. Okay. Sure. Sure.

82
00:04:45,770 --> 00:04:46,430
Take your time.

83
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:47,630
Take your time, guys.

84
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:49,600
Not bad.

85
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,310
It's so big.

86
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,159
Okay, thanks.

87
00:04:58,190 --> 00:04:59,630
I really envy you.

88
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,000
You live so freely.

89
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,120
You can go wherever you want

90
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,520
and do whatever you want.

91
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,190
And now you have

92
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:07,450
such a handsome boyfriend spoiling you.

93
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,600
Enough.

94
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:12,170
People really are different.

95
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,160
Growing up,

96
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,690
you haven't suffered much.

97
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,360
Well,

98
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:19,000
I got divorced
and am about leaving my hometown.

99
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,750
Is that what you call

100
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:21,000
"haven't suffered much"?

101
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,560
Let's not talk about unhappy things.

102
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,480
Look how impressive you are today.

103
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,430
Your brother and sister-in-law

104
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,720
threw such a lively party for you.

105
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,160
All your relatives and friends are here.

106
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,000
Don't they hope

107
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,560
that you'll have a better life?

108
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,510
Of course.

109
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,950
I can't let those

110
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:35,350
who are waiting to laugh at me
get their way.

111
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:39,010
I also sent an invitation to Tang Hong'en.

112
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,480
Why did you invite him?

113
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,390
Is that appropriate?

114
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:46,600
Don't be so old-fashioned.

115
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,270
What's inappropriate about it?

116
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,000
It's just

117
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,130
a farewell banquet.

118
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,920
This is very normal abroad.

119
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:54,159
Besides, George knows about it.

120
00:05:55,340 --> 00:05:56,870
I just want Tang Hong'en

121
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:57,390
to know

122
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,920
that I will live better without him.

123
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:02,750
So,

124
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:05,190
is he coming? Did he agree?

125
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,360
I invited him graciously.

126
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:08,430
As a mayor,

127
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,560
would he be so petty?

128
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:12,120
Cheers.

129
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,840
Mom, you look really beautiful.

130
00:06:26,070 --> 00:06:28,360
It's the pearl earrings that look good.

131
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,190
They are so big.

132
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,040
They must have been expensive.

133
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,700
Not really.

134
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:35,430
Just to attend

135
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,040
someone else's farewell banquet,

136
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,270
we wasted so much energy

137
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,530
and spent so much money

138
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,070
just to prove a point.

139
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,960
It feels like such a loss.

140
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,070
Mom,

141
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,430
the fact that you think this way

142
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,360
shows that you

143
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,870
no longer care about Ji Ya.

144
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,390
Besides, she

145
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,720
really isn't someone

146
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,270
worth competing with.

147
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:54,680
But what you just said isn't right.

148
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,750
We're not spending this money on Ji Ya.

149
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,430
We're spending it on ourselves.

150
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:00,360
Women should dress up for themselves.

151
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,240
That way, when you look at yourself,

152
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,040
you'll feel refreshed.

153
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,970
Don't you think?

154
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:04,920
Besides,

155
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,190
money is earned

156
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,390
to be spent, isn't it?

157
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,510
Even if Ji Ya looks

158
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:09,510
rich and elegant,

159
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,800
she's spending her family's

160
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,430
and her American boyfriend's money.

161
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:14,120
We spend the money we earn ourselves.

162
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,160
We can spend it with confidence,

163
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:15,630
right?

164
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,870
I don't think this lipstick suits you.

165
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:20,800
Let me change it for you.

166
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,480
Not suit me?

167
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,630
Try this one.

168
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,920
Xiaolan

169
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,430
is doing Fen's makeup.

170
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:38,950
Yes.

171
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,750
You'll have to wait a bit longer.

172
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,240
Okay.

173
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,270
You look

174
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,360
quite anxious, huh?

175
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:53,120
I'm not anxious.

176
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,450
I'm just looking forward to it.

177
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,930
If you're not anxious, have a seat.

178
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,360
Okay, okay.

179
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,970
Have some water.

180
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,660
I'll have some water with you.

181
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,680
Next, please welcome

182
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,240
Comrade Liu Fen!

183
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,480
What do you think?

184
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,080
Is it okay?

185
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:27,850
Beautiful.

186
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,910
You are truly beautiful.

187
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,950
Graceful and charming.

188
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:32,830
Like a goddess.

189
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:35,070
Adored by all, loved by flowers,

190
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,970
so cute even cars would swerve.

191
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:40,080
This bracelet...

192
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:42,630
Granny Yu,

193
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,330
this is yours, isn't it?

194
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,040
Thank you.

195
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:49,000
At the farewell banquet,

196
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,150
how should I behave?

197
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:52,200
Whatever you do is fine.

198
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,790
If you see someone you like,

199
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,480
just chat with them.

200
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:58,480
If you don't like them
or feel uncomfortable,

201
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,480
just ignore them.

202
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,840
Just be yourself.

203
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,030
Okay.

204
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,700
Granny Yu.

205
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:04,760
We're heading out.

206
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,240
Okay.

207
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,720
We're leaving, Xiaolan.

208
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,250
Bye-bye.

209
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:09,630
Wish you success.

210
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:13,910
Okay.

211
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,020
Let me do it.

212
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,440
That bracelet is really nice.

213
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,370
Do you have another one? I want one too.

214
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,570
What are you looking at?

215
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,670
Get to work now.

216
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:04,960
Liu Fen?

217
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,510
Hello, everyone.

218
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,760
I am Ji Ya's brother.

219
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,750
This is my wife, Caihong.

220
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:16,570
[Ms. Ji Ya's Farewell Banquet]

221
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,270
Today, my wife,

222
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,150
Ya,

223
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,670
and I would like to thank

224
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:18,870
all our friends and family for coming.

225
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,330
Since today

226
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,840
is Ya's farewell banquet,

227
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,060
let's invite Ya to say a few words.

228
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,160
Who knows when

229
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,670
she'll be back next time.

230
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,070
Thank you, everyone.

231
00:10:35,270 --> 00:10:37,080
Since my brother asked me to speak,

232
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,030
I'll keep it brief.

233
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:40,280
You are all

234
00:10:40,290 --> 00:10:41,720
my closest elders

235
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:43,430
and friends here in China.

236
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,870
Although

237
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,000
I've been back for a while,

238
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:49,760
I've been so busy with trivial matters

239
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,080
that I haven't been able

240
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,360
to properly get together with everyone.

241
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,150
And now, in the blink of an eye,

242
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:56,150
I'm going back to America.

243
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,830
I'd like to take this opportunity today

244
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:02,000
to propose a toast to everyone.

245
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,510
I wish you all smooth sailing

246
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,720
and ever-improving days ahead.

247
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,510
Thank you all.

248
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:06,790
Come on.

249
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,000
-Ever-improving days ahead.
-Ever-improving days ahead.

250
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,480
Cheers.

251
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,270
Thank you.

252
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:12,790
Ya,

253
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,510
this gentleman beside you,

254
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,360
shouldn't you

255
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,480
introduce him to us?

256
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,120
Yeah.

257
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:19,280
Do you have some good news to announce?

258
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:19,910
Okay.

259
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:20,910
I saw

260
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,710
the diamond ring on your finger.

261
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,480
Let me introduce him to everyone.

262
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,790
This is George.

263
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,630
He is my fiancé,

264
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:31,540
because

265
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,510
I just accepted his proposal.

266
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:35,790
Hello, everyone.

267
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,200
Thank you. Thank you, everyone.

268
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,050
Hello, Sir.

269
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,540
Do you have a reservation?

270
00:11:46,730 --> 00:11:47,470
We are here

271
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:48,870
for Ms. Ji Ya's farewell banquet.

272
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:49,630
Okay, it's in this hall.

273
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:50,440
This way, please.

274
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:50,790
Okay.

275
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,630
If you change your mind

276
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,750
and don't want to go in,

277
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,010
we can leave right now.

278
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,360
It's okay.

279
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,350
I've decided to come.

280
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,140
Let's go in.

281
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:12,240
Why is he here?

282
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:14,750
Ya,

283
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:15,710
why is he here?

284
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,790
It's interesting that he's here.

285
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,530
That's her ex-husband.

286
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,240
I thought people here

287
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,370
were conservative.

288
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:26,270
But... apparently not.

289
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:29,910
Ji Ya and her ex seem to
have handled their relationship

290
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,150
so quite well.

291
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,750
Hold her back, quick.

292
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,870
Mayor Tang.

293
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,130
It is Mayor Tang.

294
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:35,810
Mayor Tang.

295
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,750
Tang,

296
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,930
what do you mean?

297
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,320
Nothing much.

298
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:59,080
Ji Ya invited me repeatedly

299
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:00,240
to attend

300
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,720
her farewell banquet
before she returns to America.

301
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,320
So I brought my family along.

302
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,440
Since she's been so generous,

303
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,370
I can't be petty.

304
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,380
Is there a problem?

305
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,730
Are you okay?

306
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:21,360
How could I possibly feel well?

307
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:24,630
Didn't you see he brought her

308
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,480
to my farewell banquet?

309
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:29,030
I'm leaving this country tomorrow.

310
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:31,240
This is my last meeting,

311
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:34,480
and he couldn't spare me
a shred of dignity.

312
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,330
Do you want to stay?

313
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:40,870
I'm okay.

314
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:48,510
You just asked me

315
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,480
if there was a problem, didn't you?

316
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,200
No problem.

317
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,240
I'm glad you came.

318
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,200
I just didn't expect

319
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:57,600
you to bring an extra person.

320
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,530
Since you're already here,

321
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,790
let's have a drink together.

322
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,960
Liu Fen doesn't usually drink much.

323
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,570
I'll drink for her.

324
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,480
I can drink.

325
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:19,840
No need to down it.

326
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,970
Just a sip is enough.

327
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:26,550
Ji Ya.

328
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,600
We wish you

329
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,150
a happy life in America.

330
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:31,960
May you and George

331
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:34,000
be together for a long time.

332
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,880
Tang Hong'en,

333
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,390
I was kind enough to invite you

334
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,270
to my farewell banquet!

335
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,330
And what did you do?

336
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:54,030
You brought

337
00:14:54,030 --> 00:14:55,000
a shady woman here!

338
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:55,550
Who knows which village

339
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:56,600
she came from?

340
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,480
I don't even know

341
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,630
what kind of low-class,

342
00:14:58,630 --> 00:14:59,390
shameful methods she used

343
00:14:59,390 --> 00:14:59,790
to seduce you!

344
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:00,630
Don't be so vicious!

345
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:01,670
And you just brought her here like this!

346
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:02,150
Enough!

347
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:06,150
It doesn't matter what you say about me,

348
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:06,910
but you can't,

349
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,030
in public,

350
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,120
fabricate facts

351
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,960
and tarnish Comrade Liu Fen's reputation!

352
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,020
Alright, alright.

353
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:13,510
You claim to be

354
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:14,910
from a scholarly family,

355
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,930
so please watch your language.

356
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,240
This event today

357
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:19,320
is hosted by you.

358
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,440
All these friends

359
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,550
are here, because of you,

360
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:22,910
to sincerely

361
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,960
bid you farewell.

362
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:26,600
So please have some self-respect.

363
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,000
I...

364
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:27,790
Tang.

365
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,960
Don't think just because you're the mayor,

366
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,490
you can talk to us like that!

367
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,840
There are so many people watching.

368
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,770
There are so many people watching.

369
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,010
There are so many people watching.

370
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,360
Let me speak for myself.

371
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,030
Ji Ya,

372
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,390
you're right.

373
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,390
I am from a village.

374
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:49,590
But that doesn't mean

375
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,220
I'm worse than others,

376
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,950
or lower than others.

377
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,650
The countryside raised us.

378
00:15:56,050 --> 00:15:57,080
Although it didn't give us

379
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,080
material wealth,

380
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,320
the countryside taught us

381
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:01,980
diligence,

382
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:02,800
courage,

383
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,470
and defiance.

384
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:07,330
We refuse to yield to those

385
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:08,870
who look down on us.

386
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:11,150
We refuse to accept when people say

387
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:12,010
we are unworthy

388
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:12,950
or incapable.

389
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:15,510
So,

390
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,080
we strive

391
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,880
to succeed just to prove a point.

392
00:16:20,450 --> 00:16:21,480
Every penny Xiaolan and I

393
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,670
have earned

394
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,750
came from our own hard work.

395
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,750
It's clean

396
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,320
and honest.

397
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,000
In terms of backgrounds,

398
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,320
since you were born into

399
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,650
such a powerful family,

400
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:35,550
I can't compare with you.

401
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:37,140
But

402
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:39,080
after all these years of hard work,

403
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,910
I dare say

404
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,540
that the current me

405
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,520
is no worse than you.

406
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:52,320
Well said.

407
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,320
No matter who I am now,

408
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,530
whether I'm a leader or not,

409
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:00,920
please don't forget

410
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,720
that I'm also from the countryside.

411
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:06,790
Friends,

412
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,740
I apologize for today.

413
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,069
Let's go.

414
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:12,829
I'll take you

415
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:15,020
to your favorite tea restaurant.

416
00:17:16,109 --> 00:17:17,109
Whatever you say.

417
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:38,800
Let's go.

418
00:17:39,610 --> 00:17:40,240
Calm down.

419
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:48,270
I'm truly sorry

420
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:49,270
about how things

421
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:50,790
turned out today

422
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,000
and made you so embarrassed.

423
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:54,650
Actually, Ji Ya

424
00:17:54,790 --> 00:17:56,880
wanted fame and fortune through me,

425
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:58,800
but I couldn't satisfy her.

426
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,360
That's why we separated.

427
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,590
But I think

428
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,010
the end of a marriage

429
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,470
isn't the end of life.

430
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,350
If one is lucky enough

431
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,340
to meet someone they like,

432
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,650
someone suitable,

433
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:15,360
that is the beginning of true happiness.

434
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:17,830
Fen,

435
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,640
I think

436
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,160
I'm so fortunate

437
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,510
to have met you.

438
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:26,770
It all started when you fed me
that first spoonful of porridge.

439
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:29,200
Today,

440
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,360
asking you to the banquet

441
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,690
was out of my selfish motives.

442
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,040
Because the friends who came

443
00:18:36,650 --> 00:18:38,380
are people we knew from before.

444
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,880
Since you're willing to come with me,

445
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:41,590
our relationship

446
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:42,590
is out in the open.

447
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,310
I know

448
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,550
you are actually someone

449
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:48,250
who likes to keep a low profile.

450
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:48,790
For my sake,

451
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:50,450
you made such a big sacrifice,

452
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,820
and I'm really grateful for that.

453
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:54,960
And just now inside,

454
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:56,410
the words you spoke

455
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,270
really shocked me.

456
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,350
You are so kind

457
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:03,200
and so independent.

458
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,290
You are so kind to others

459
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:06,830
that for a moment,

460
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,440
I wanted, in front of everyone,

461
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,770
to ask if you'd marry me.

462
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:12,790
But I felt

463
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,880
that would

464
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,400
embarrass you,

465
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,480
so I dropped

466
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,160
the idea.

467
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,500
Let's take it slow.

468
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:22,830
Everything

469
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,510
will go at your pace.

470
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:26,530
I'm willing to wait.

471
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,390
I'm willing to wait forever.

472
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,880
I also want to use this period of time

473
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:33,880
to get my affairs

474
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,090
in better order,

475
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,030
so that you can

476
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:38,560
let go of all your concerns,

477
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:39,840
truly accept me,

478
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:42,000
and truly, from your heart,

479
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,200
want to be with me.

480
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:45,920
I can't guarantee that in the future,

481
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:46,920
I can give you

482
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,270
a luxurious life,

483
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,090
but I can guarantee

484
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:52,150
that I will be good to you,

485
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,450
and even better to your family.

486
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,300
I will give every penny I earn,

487
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:59,320
such as salary and bonuses,

488
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:00,550
to you.

489
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:01,880
And this money

490
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:02,880
is all clean,

491
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,400
so you can spend it

492
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,040
with your head held high.

493
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:08,600
I will help you earn respect

494
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:09,760
and make you feel

495
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,330
that being with this man

496
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,200
is worth it.

497
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,610
I can make my own money.

498
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:19,930
I don't need to spend yours.

499
00:20:30,610 --> 00:20:31,610
I'm really sorry.

500
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,350
I'm really sorry, really.

501
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:33,000
We'll be going now.

502
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:33,750
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

503
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:35,160
Ji Lin, look at this mess.

504
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:36,580
You should comfort

505
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:37,560
Ji Ya first.

506
00:20:37,590 --> 00:20:37,880
Okay, okay.

507
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,590
We're leaving now.

508
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:39,680
Okay. Sorry you had to see that.

509
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,510
Sorry for the drama.

510
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:41,570
Goodbye. Goodbye.

511
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,460
Ya,

512
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:01,950
have you lost your mind?

513
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:02,880
You invited him,

514
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,350
and what are you angry about?

515
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,160
Have you considered

516
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,070
my feelings

517
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,470
and George's feelings?

518
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,310
I'm talking to you.

519
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,340
You can disrespect yourself,

520
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,240
and you can

521
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,240
disrespect me,

522
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,270
but what gives you the right

523
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,680
to disrespect your brother?

524
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,830
You just do whatever makes you happy,

525
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:20,960
making your brother

526
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,510
clean up your mess time and again.

527
00:21:22,510 --> 00:21:23,680
Look at yourself.

528
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,310
Without the Ji family

529
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:26,040
or George,

530
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,510
what could you actually do?

531
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:28,710
You fail at business,

532
00:21:28,740 --> 00:21:30,160
and you fail to keep your family together.

533
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:32,290
You trample on everyone who loves you!

534
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,780
Alright, alright.

535
00:21:34,590 --> 00:21:36,350
You're going back to America
tomorrow anyway.

536
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:37,550
Do whatever you want.

537
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:39,160
We can't control you anymore.

538
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,490
Once you get to America,

539
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:41,990
don't ever come back!

540
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:43,230
Let's go.

541
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,510
Ji Ya.

542
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:53,270
Can you tell me

543
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:54,400
what was that about?

544
00:22:10,070 --> 00:22:10,750
George.

545
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:13,590
I'm sorry.

546
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:16,000
I got you into this.

547
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:18,880
I lost control.

548
00:22:20,290 --> 00:22:23,420
I don't know what came over me.

549
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,200
Honey,

550
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:32,240
can you forgive me?

551
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:36,550
Okay.

552
00:22:38,510 --> 00:22:39,270
First of all,

553
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:42,250
I hope you'll forget about him

554
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,840
and forget about her.

555
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:45,960
We go to America.

556
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,270
It's just you and me.

557
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,920
We start a new life in America.

558
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:54,680
Okay.

559
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:57,160
I love you.

560
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,240
Are you sure?

561
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:03,880
I'm sure.

562
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:11,560
[Spring, 1992]

563
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:12,750
Ms. Yu,

564
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,060
since you're willing to meet,

565
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,710
I won't beat around the bush.

566
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,790
You are the General Manager of Elegance

567
00:23:18,790 --> 00:23:19,550
in name only.

568
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:22,320
Actually, you don't get to make decisions.

569
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:27,000
The real boss of Elegance now is Vivi,

570
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:28,350
right?

571
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,240
These are internal matters

572
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:31,510
at Elegance.

573
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:34,080
I don't need to explain them to you.

574
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,200
True.

575
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,440
Your internal affairs

576
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,770
are none of my business.

577
00:23:51,090 --> 00:23:52,120
[Detailed Evidence Report on Elegance's
Alleged Infringement]

578
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,150
[by Copying Luna Clothing Designs]

579
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:00,750
What do you mean?

580
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:02,030
Are you going to sue us?

581
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:02,830
That's right.

582
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:05,030
Since last quarter, Elegance

583
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,890
has been copying Luna's designs.

584
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:08,160
Ms. Yu,

585
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,360
don't rush to deny it.

586
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,750
We have sufficient evidence

587
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,720
to prove it.

588
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:12,830
Besides,

589
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:14,550
you hired people

590
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:16,640
to sabotage the construction
of Luna's store,

591
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,440
cut the power,

592
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:18,940
and smash windows.

593
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,160
These things happened

594
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:22,090
before you got to where you are now,

595
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,550
so you might not know.

596
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:25,520
But we have plenty of evidence.

597
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,310
Ms. Yu.

598
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:32,750
You're just an employee.

599
00:24:33,030 --> 00:24:34,920
I don't want to make things hard for you.

600
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:35,680
However,

601
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,680
please tell Vivi for me.

602
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,500
After all these years,

603
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,400
she hasn't improved at all.

604
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:43,030
She's still using

605
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:44,240
such dirty tricks.

606
00:24:45,030 --> 00:24:46,720
She really hasn't let me down.

607
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:48,730
Three days.

608
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,720
I'll give you 3 days

609
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:53,270
to take down all the plagiarized works.

610
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:54,240
Otherwise,

611
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:57,620
I promise I'll sue you into bankruptcy.

612
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:04,480
Do you have any other questions?

613
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:05,950
I can answer them for you.

614
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:08,110
I have no further questions.

615
00:25:08,350 --> 00:25:10,550
I generally understand the situation.

616
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:12,350
Excuse me,

617
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,090
I'll take my leave.

618
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:21,310
Mr. Zhou,

619
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:22,440
nice teamwork.

620
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:26,450
Xiaolan.

621
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:28,550
Xia Ziyu

622
00:25:28,550 --> 00:25:30,350
has stayed in Gangdao all along,

623
00:25:30,360 --> 00:25:31,440
but she seems to know

624
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,570
every move you make.

625
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,810
I am also very curious about Xia Ziyu.

626
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:37,920
Next time I see Du Zhaohui,

627
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:38,920
I definitely have to

628
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,040
ask him all about

629
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:41,730
his future young stepmother.

630
00:25:42,270 --> 00:25:43,360
Will Xia Ziyu

631
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:45,080
really marry Du Chengrong?

632
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:46,830
As long as there is a chance,

633
00:25:46,830 --> 00:25:48,560
she will definitely marry him.

634
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,310
Only by becoming Mrs. Du

635
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,200
will she feel secure.

636
00:25:53,970 --> 00:25:54,790
Alright, let's not talk about her.

637
00:25:54,790 --> 00:25:55,590
Let's go home.

638
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:56,750
Ms. Xia.

639
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:58,550
You forgot again.

640
00:25:59,070 --> 00:26:01,270
We are going to the flower market today.

641
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:03,670
Oh, right.

642
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,620
It's a good thing you're here.

643
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:06,360
Let's go.

644
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:09,510
I've been in Shengcheng for so many years,

645
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:10,740
but I've never visited the flower market.

646
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:12,200
I didn't expect it to be so lively.

647
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:14,070
I should have brought my mom along.

648
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:15,270
Do you see anything you like?

649
00:26:15,270 --> 00:26:15,800
This one.

650
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:17,960
Here you go.

651
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:18,620
You like it?

652
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:19,550
Sir,

653
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:21,070
this is a New Year mandarin orange tree,
right?

654
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:22,000
Yes, it is.

655
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:22,750
But

656
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:23,750
you can't eat them.

657
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,680
You can hang some

658
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:25,920
small red envelopes on it

659
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,110
with just a few cents

660
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,270
or dimes inside,

661
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,280
for good luck.

662
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,450
This is quite interesting.

663
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:33,030
Okay, we'll look around some more.

664
00:26:33,030 --> 00:26:33,790
Sure, sure.

665
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,790
This Lucky Bamboo isn't bad either.

666
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:37,070
We can buy 2 pots for the office.

667
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:37,350
Yes.

668
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,110
Pay for it!

669
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,110
Do you like it?

670
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:57,070
Ms. Xia.

671
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,680
What a coincidence.

672
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:00,480
Here for the New Year shopping?

673
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:02,610
Let me wish you an early Happy New Year.

674
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:04,480
Happy New Year. Happy New Year.

675
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:07,520
Since we've run into each other,

676
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:08,350
I have a few words

677
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:09,550
to say to you, Ms. Xia.

678
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,350
I know

679
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:13,610
you are quite close to the Bai family.

680
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:14,440
Please

681
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,790
pass a message to Bai Zhenzhu for me.

682
00:27:17,350 --> 00:27:18,830
Because she is a woman,

683
00:27:19,030 --> 00:27:20,630
I have been going easy on her.

684
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,240
However,

685
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,070
tell her not to take things

686
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,400
so seriously.

687
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:25,750
Otherwise,

688
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:27,720
I won't be polite anymore.

689
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:31,440
Are you asking me to stop Bai Zhenzhu

690
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:33,340
from stealing your business?

691
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:34,920
Mr. Ke,

692
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,880
in business,
it's every person for themselves.

693
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,740
Why should I suddenly interfere?

694
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,400
If you want both sides to sit down

695
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,600
and negotiate peace,

696
00:27:42,770 --> 00:27:43,850
to divide

697
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:45,210
business territories,

698
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:46,410
you have to show

699
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,040
an attitude of negotiation.

700
00:27:48,070 --> 00:27:48,830
Last time,

701
00:27:48,830 --> 00:27:50,750
you caused trouble
at Zhenzhu's birthday party.

702
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,400
This time,

703
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:53,350
you're making a baffling demand of me.

704
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,110
Ke Yixiong,

705
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,910
can't you be reasonable?

706
00:27:59,590 --> 00:27:59,960
Okay.

707
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:00,720
Okay.

708
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:02,270
Ms. Xia,

709
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,640
then tell Bai Zhenzhu

710
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:05,880
to wait and see.

711
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:08,810
Enjoy your stroll.

712
00:28:08,830 --> 00:28:10,230
The goods here are great.

713
00:28:10,370 --> 00:28:11,150
Buy a lot.

714
00:28:11,310 --> 00:28:11,880
Goodbye!

715
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:12,730
Goodbye.

716
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:15,550
When did things get so tense

717
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:17,350
between Zhenzhu and Ke Yixiong?

718
00:28:17,530 --> 00:28:19,350
After the brothers
at the Bai Martial Arts School

719
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,650
have suffered for years,

720
00:28:20,650 --> 00:28:21,680
they finally found a way

721
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:23,010
to improve their lives.

722
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,510
And with Zhenzhu leading them,

723
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:26,480
naturally, they're not afraid to fight.

724
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,480
Ke Yixiong can't call

725
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,140
every hooligan in Longcheng.

726
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,550
And without guns,

727
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:31,720
naturally, they can't win

728
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:33,510
against the brothers
from the Bai Martial Arts School.

729
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:35,110
He must have taken a beating.

730
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:38,450
We still need to tell Zhenzhu,

731
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,810
so she can be prepared.

732
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:41,830
When we see her at New Year's,

733
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:42,760
I'll remind her.

734
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:43,840
Oh right.

735
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:47,270
Since you're not returning
to Jingcheng this year,

736
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,670
won't Mrs. Guan be angry?

737
00:28:49,790 --> 00:28:51,080
Ms. Guan Hui'e

738
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,480
is very open-minded this time.

739
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,880
She said she wanted to come to Shengcheng

740
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,810
to see how Southerners celebrate.

741
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:56,360
Alright.

742
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:08,400
Granny Yu.

743
00:29:09,070 --> 00:29:09,920
My goodness.

744
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:10,790
You haven't forgotten

745
00:29:10,790 --> 00:29:12,640
a single thing I taught you.

746
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:13,160
How does it look?

747
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:13,820
Beautiful.

748
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,790
I remember you telling me

749
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:17,920
that when you steam

750
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:18,610
these buns,

751
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:19,840
you make them blossom

752
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,160
for good luck.

753
00:29:21,180 --> 00:29:21,860
Exactly.

754
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:24,510
Birdcage shape and Grain mouth.

755
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:26,920
I heard from Fen

756
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,110
that in a while,

757
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,770
you're moving to Shengcheng.

758
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,960
After Tao finishes this semester,

759
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:33,750
we'll move here next semester.

760
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:35,000
Let him start high school

761
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:35,860
in Shengcheng.

762
00:29:36,270 --> 00:29:37,720
It's a pity Xiaolan's house

763
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:38,850
isn't finished yet.

764
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,480
Otherwise, when you arrive,

765
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:42,310
you could live in your own place.

766
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:43,440
As long as the family

767
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:44,950
can live together, it's fine.

768
00:29:44,950 --> 00:29:45,640
Whether the house

769
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,720
belongs to someone else

770
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:47,590
or us

771
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,880
doesn't really matter.

772
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,210
Look at you and Xiaolan,

773
00:29:50,550 --> 00:29:51,330
living with Granny Yu.

774
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:53,130
Aren't you practically family?

775
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:53,960
That's right.

776
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:54,890
Let me tell you,

777
00:29:55,110 --> 00:29:56,310
when you move here,

778
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:58,680
I'll teach you a few more tricks.

779
00:29:58,880 --> 00:29:59,940
That's wonderful.

780
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,480
Granny Yu, Aunt, Mom,

781
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:03,240
we're back.

782
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:04,270
Tao, you're back.

783
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:06,030
It's great to be near the sea.

784
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,270
Everything is fresh.

785
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:07,960
It's fresh.

786
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:08,740
Go to the kitchen,

787
00:30:08,740 --> 00:30:10,030
and fill the big basin with water.

788
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:11,090
Don't let them die.

789
00:30:11,090 --> 00:30:11,920
When we cook them tonight,

790
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,000
they'll still be alive.

791
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,110
Wash the chicken and everything

792
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:14,830
and cut them up.

793
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,790
We'll use them for soup later.

794
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:16,230
Okay.

795
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:17,110
Okay, Mom.

796
00:30:18,930 --> 00:30:19,920
Xiaolan and Zhou Cheng

797
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:20,830
have gone to pick up his mother.

798
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:22,230
They should be back soon.

799
00:30:25,550 --> 00:30:26,030
How is it?

800
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:26,880
This is good. This is good.

801
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,400
Looks good?

802
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,350
It's fine. Just right.

803
00:30:28,350 --> 00:30:29,810
I'm pasting the left side.

804
00:30:30,390 --> 00:30:31,160
Watch it for me.

805
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,490
Make sure it's aligned.

806
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:33,590
Look.

807
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,070
A bit more...

808
00:30:34,070 --> 00:30:34,480
Is that okay?

809
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,270
A little lower.

810
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:35,720
Lower.

811
00:30:35,830 --> 00:30:36,490
Okay. Okay.

812
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,410
That's good.

813
00:30:39,170 --> 00:30:40,440
The New Year should be lively.

814
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,750
Ask You Li to come too.

815
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:44,370
She's at the hospital with her mom.

816
00:30:44,530 --> 00:30:45,240
I told her

817
00:30:45,270 --> 00:30:46,930
I'd bring her New Year's dinner later.

818
00:30:46,930 --> 00:30:47,560
She told me

819
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:48,940
her mom is responding now.

820
00:30:48,940 --> 00:30:49,880
Sometimes when she speaks,

821
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:50,740
she even cries.

822
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:51,920
She said she never thought

823
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:53,580
she'd be so happy to see tears.

824
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:55,640
Wei.

825
00:30:55,830 --> 00:30:56,590
Now she tells you

826
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,790
everything.

827
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:59,640
You're almost there.

828
00:30:59,830 --> 00:31:00,640
No, no.

829
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,070
Let me tell you.

830
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,310
The revolution has not yet succeeded.

831
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,710
I still need to work hard.

832
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,580
Why didn't you ask San to come?

833
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:07,550
San isn't from Shengcheng.

834
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:09,480
He has to spend the New Year
with his family.

835
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,210
Unlike you, hanging around here.

836
00:31:11,210 --> 00:31:12,570
How can you call it hanging around?

837
00:31:12,570 --> 00:31:14,890
Xiaolan's home is my home.

838
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:17,790
Cheng.

839
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:19,830
Hello, Mrs. Guan.

840
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:21,480
Cheng, you're here.

841
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,400
Xiaolan.

842
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:23,310
Mrs. Guan. Hello, Mrs. Guan.

843
00:31:23,310 --> 00:31:24,030
You're here.

844
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:24,750
Happy New Year.

845
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,960
I heard everything,

846
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,680
Wei.

847
00:31:27,210 --> 00:31:28,350
Aren't you afraid I'll tell your mom

848
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:29,350
and second uncle?

849
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:30,640
Hello, Mrs. Guan.

850
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,270
Hello, hello.

851
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:31,790
Mrs. Guan,

852
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:33,270
you won't sell me out.

853
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:34,480
Besides, I didn't go back this time,

854
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:35,600
and they didn't come to catch me.

855
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:37,000
You must have explained it to her.

856
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,110
They didn't come,

857
00:31:38,110 --> 00:31:39,750
but they sent me to inspect.

858
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,200
You'd better behave.

859
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:41,930
Absolutely.

860
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:42,720
Well, Cheng,

861
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:43,510
I'll get them!

862
00:31:43,510 --> 00:31:44,070
Don't, don't!

863
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:44,960
I'll get them! Let me do that!

864
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,640
Here, here.

865
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,070
I'll get them! Let me do that!

866
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:47,750
You're here.

867
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:49,110
Fen, Fen, Fen.

868
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,010
Was the trip smooth?

869
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:51,890
Very smooth.

870
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,030
You know, Shengcheng

871
00:31:53,030 --> 00:31:54,160
isn't cold at all.

872
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,310
It's so comfortable.

873
00:31:55,310 --> 00:31:56,270
-Really.
-Quick,

874
00:31:56,270 --> 00:31:56,920
come in.

875
00:32:02,310 --> 00:32:03,000
Wei.

876
00:32:03,250 --> 00:32:04,320
Don't eat too much.

877
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:04,920
There's so much food.

878
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,750
Today,

879
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,480
we have a mix of North and South.

880
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:09,040
We have customs from both.

881
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:09,830
At 12 o'clock at night,

882
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:10,750
we still have to boil dumplings.

883
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:11,200
Later,

884
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,800
I have to bring food to You Li.

885
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:13,830
With this round trip,

886
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:14,760
I can eat 2 plates

887
00:32:14,790 --> 00:32:15,590
of the dumplings at 12.

888
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,190
It's fine.

889
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:17,400
Fen.

890
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,310
At this scene right now,

891
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,840
guess what I'm thinking of?

892
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,110
What?

893
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,240
Are you thinking of

894
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,960
the whole village crowding together

895
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:27,030
on the threshing floor
to watch the Chinese New Year Gala?

896
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:27,630
Is that it?

897
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:30,200
My wife knows me best.

898
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:31,770
I'm not like you.

899
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:33,480
I don't like dwelling on the past.

900
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,550
Look, our lives

901
00:32:34,550 --> 00:32:36,000
are getting better and better.

902
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:37,240
Now, every day when I wake up,

903
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:39,300
I only think about better days ahead.

904
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:39,840
Right.

905
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,080
Well said, Auntie.

906
00:32:41,110 --> 00:32:41,920
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

907
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,550
-Cheers.
-Thank you, Xiaolan.

908
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:44,880
To our better future!

909
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,440
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

910
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,310
These buildings

911
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:55,880
are getting taller and taller now.

912
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:56,680
In the future,

913
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:57,660
this kind of view

914
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:59,310
might be hard to come by.

915
00:32:59,830 --> 00:33:00,350
Mom,

916
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,310
nowadays, buildings

917
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:02,550
can also have good views.

918
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:04,160
It depends on whether the builder

919
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,240
puts her heart into it.

920
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:06,310
Look at you.

921
00:33:06,340 --> 00:33:10,110
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

922
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,680
Mrs. Guan, don't worry.

923
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:09,880
The building I build
will definitely have great views.

924
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:10,590
Definitely.

925
00:33:10,590 --> 00:33:11,000
Right.

926
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:13,560
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

927
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:12,440
Yes.

928
00:33:13,270 --> 00:33:13,750
Mom.

929
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:16,630
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

930
00:33:14,550 --> 00:33:15,640
Didn't Mr. Tang tell you

931
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:17,040
if he can come back or not?

932
00:33:17,790 --> 00:33:19,590
He's busiest during the holidays.

933
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:23,540
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

934
00:33:19,830 --> 00:33:21,960
He has to visit the community
to bring warmth.

935
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:22,560
It's okay.

936
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:23,830
Let me,

937
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:26,030
your sweet daughter, bring you warmth!

938
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:26,950
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

939
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,830
Xiaolan is the best.

940
00:33:26,970 --> 00:33:30,720
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

941
00:33:27,830 --> 00:33:29,510
It's better to have a daughter.

942
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:30,830
I'm almost done eating.

943
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:32,110
I'll go bring her the food while it's hot.

944
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:33,680
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

945
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:33,310
As for You's portion,

946
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:34,680
I packed it separately.

947
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:35,350
It's in the wok.

948
00:33:34,890 --> 00:33:37,460
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

949
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,490
I'll get it. I'll get it.

950
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,310
After Mom

951
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:40,710
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

952
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:40,830
marries Mr. Tang,

953
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:42,240
she'll have to move

954
00:33:41,430 --> 00:33:46,310
♪ Our youth ♪

955
00:33:42,270 --> 00:33:43,400
to his place, right?

956
00:33:44,110 --> 00:33:45,440
Then poor me.

957
00:33:46,330 --> 00:33:49,860
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

958
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,550
Then...

959
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,460
let's get married too?

960
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:53,260
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

961
00:33:50,680 --> 00:33:51,160
Great.

962
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:53,790
Okay.

963
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:56,280
♪ We never give up ♪

964
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,200
But promise me,

965
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:56,640
after we get married,

966
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,350
I still want to live here with Granny Yu.

967
00:33:56,900 --> 00:34:00,120
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

968
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,140
Otherwise, she'll miss me,

969
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:03,370
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

970
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,030
right?

971
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,440
Exactly.

972
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,750
This is your home.

973
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:06,790
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

974
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,200
Xiaolan, Zhou,

975
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:07,510
we're waiting for

976
00:34:06,820 --> 00:34:09,870
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

977
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:08,510
your big day.

978
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:10,960
You have to keep your word.

979
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:13,280
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

980
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,710
The elders are all here today.

981
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:13,920
You can't lie to us.

982
00:34:13,650 --> 00:34:19,630
♪ That'd be enough ♪

983
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:14,440
Okay.

984
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:15,620
It's a deal.

985
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:16,090
Come on.

986
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:16,980
It's a deal.

987
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:19,840
Careful.

988
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:20,670
Got it.

989
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,510
Don't spill it.

990
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,440
I'm heading out.

991
00:34:22,719 --> 00:34:23,630
-Careful.
-Be careful.

992
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,150
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

993
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,480
Barbecue pork buns are here.

994
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,480
Happy New Year!

995
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,110
Mr. Tang.

996
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:29,030
Happy New Year!

997
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,670
The Mayor is here.

998
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,530
Happy New Year!

999
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,070
Happy New Year! Happy New Year!

1000
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,000
Come on, come on.

1001
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:34,670
Hello, Auntie.

1002
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:35,630
Sit with Fen, come on.

1003
00:34:35,630 --> 00:34:36,550
Where did you go?

1004
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:37,590
But now,

1005
00:34:37,590 --> 00:34:38,630
you're about to become

1006
00:34:38,630 --> 00:34:39,760
my brother-in-law.

1007
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:41,449
Comrade Tang.

1008
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,050
Here, take my glass.

1009
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:43,880
Drink a cup as a penalty.

1010
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,510
You must drink for being late.

1011
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,770
This is a good penalty.

1012
00:34:47,150 --> 00:34:47,880
I accept it.

1013
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:49,210
Bottoms up.

1014
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:49,920
Happy New Year.

1015
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,250
Good.

1016
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,630
That's not just accepting a penalty.

1017
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:55,429
He's clearly acknowledging
his brother-in-law.

1018
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:58,110
Mr. Tang, don't drink alone.

1019
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,570
Let's all toast together.

1020
00:34:59,590 --> 00:35:01,480
Okay, come on.

1021
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,620
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

1022
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:08,570
You must be hungry.

1023
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:09,760
Eat up.

1024
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:10,550
Okay.

1025
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:11,320
Hungry?

1026
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,070
Yes.

1027
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,730
There are barbecue pork buns.

1028
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:14,590
Look.

1029
00:35:14,890 --> 00:35:16,190
The buns have blossomed.

1030
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:17,280
They look great.

1031
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:29,360
The old me

1032
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,160
was afraid to answer

1033
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,080
questions about happiness.

1034
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,840
Not because I was being difficult,

1035
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:37,900
nor because I wanted to spite anyone,

1036
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,360
but because...

1037
00:35:39,910 --> 00:35:41,510
I didn't know how to describe

1038
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,610
things that don't belong to me.

1039
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:46,590
If you ask me

1040
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,990
to define happiness now,

1041
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,920
I might still draw a blank.

1042
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:54,000
Because happiness has no answer.

1043
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:56,410
Happiness is a tangible feeling.

1044
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:58,960
It's all these warm,

1045
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:00,810
bright moments,

1046
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,400
just like now.

1047
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:44,800
It's raining so hard.

1048
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,000
Will Zhenzhu make it?

1049
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,630
No one is answering at the shop.

1050
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:48,630
They must be closed.

1051
00:36:48,630 --> 00:36:49,960
Let's wait a bit longer.

1052
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:58,330
[Happy Life Materials]

1053
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:25,260
Where are you going, Bai Zhenzhu?

1054
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:29,880
Have you eaten yet?

1055
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:31,880
Get her!

1056
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:33,380
Get her!

1057
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:57,280
She's not returning pages
or answering calls.

1058
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:59,010
I feel like something is wrong.

1059
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,550
Let's go check.

1060
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:02,000
Okay.

1061
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,010
Hello, Ge Jian.

1062
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:09,930
Something happened to Zhenzhu.

1063
00:38:09,930 --> 00:38:10,730
Okay, I got it.

1064
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:29,640
Zhenzhu!

1065
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,020
How are you?

1066
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,000
What happened here?

1067
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,230
Zhenzhu, what happened?

1068
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:35,960
Who did this?

1069
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:37,960
It's okay. It's okay.

1070
00:38:38,850 --> 00:38:40,070
Ge Jian, take her to the hospital.

1071
00:38:40,070 --> 00:38:40,440
Okay.

1072
00:38:40,730 --> 00:38:42,730
No need. It's just flesh wounds.

1073
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:44,160
I'm already bandaged up.

1074
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:47,030
It was Ke Yixiong's gang.

1075
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:49,730
How many of them?

1076
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,620
Seven or eight.

1077
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:53,330
Seven or eight people?

1078
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:54,400
Just flesh wounds?

1079
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:55,920
They ran away after the fight?

1080
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:56,450
Zhenzhu,

1081
00:38:56,810 --> 00:38:57,630
no matter how skilled you are,

1082
00:38:57,630 --> 00:38:58,860
you couldn't have beaten off

1083
00:38:58,860 --> 00:38:59,530
7 or 8 men.

1084
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:03,280
Zhenzhu,

1085
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:04,550
at a time like this,

1086
00:39:04,550 --> 00:39:05,550
tell us the truth.

1087
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:08,800
Well...

1088
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:10,510
San was here just now.

1089
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:12,550
He fought them off.

1090
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,190
Then where is San?

1091
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,760
Has San gone to chase

1092
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,560
those people?

1093
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:20,710
Zhenzhu,

1094
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,440
even if San is skilled,

1095
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:24,030
he's outnumbered.

1096
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:25,850
Zhenzhu,

1097
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,660
San is angry right now.

1098
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,880
If he hits too hard,

1099
00:39:29,030 --> 00:39:30,830
he'll get himself into trouble.

1100
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:34,110
San didn't chase those thugs.

1101
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,240
He knew it must be

1102
00:39:35,250 --> 00:39:36,530
Ke Yixiong's doing.

1103
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:39,070
He went straight to find Ke Yixiong.

1104
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,190
San said...

1105
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,940
however many injuries I have,

1106
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:45,070
he'll give the same to Ke Yixiong.

1107
00:39:45,070 --> 00:39:46,530
He went to find Ke Yixiong?

1108
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:50,490
Xiaolan, I'm going to find San.

1109
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:51,480
I'll go with you.

1110
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,210
No need. You stay with them.

1111
00:39:52,210 --> 00:39:52,920
Be careful!

1112
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:53,880
Stay safe!

1113
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:03,630
Ke Yixiong's stronghold in Longcheng

1114
00:40:03,630 --> 00:40:05,520
has always been that mahjong parlor.

1115
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,210
When San gets there,

1116
00:40:06,210 --> 00:40:08,010
he'll have to look for him there.

1117
00:40:16,070 --> 00:40:16,530
Ms. Xia,

1118
00:40:16,670 --> 00:40:17,200
Zhenzhu,

1119
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,840
you two talk. I'll keep watch outside.

1120
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,300
Thanks.

1121
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:24,410
Zhenzhu,

1122
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:26,230
come home with me tonight.

1123
00:40:26,230 --> 00:40:28,560
I don't feel safe leaving you by yourself.

1124
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:30,800
Look at me, Xiaolan.

1125
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,510
I'll definitely behave myself

1126
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:34,070
and go home to sleep.

1127
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:36,150
If I go back with you and make noise,

1128
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:38,150
Granny Yu won't be able to rest well.

1129
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:40,030
Granny Yu doesn't mind a little noise.

1130
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:41,280
Stop making excuses.

1131
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,880
I didn't expect this either.

1132
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:50,080
Ke Yixiong is a sore loser.

1133
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:51,710
He acted like a cornered rat.

1134
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:53,710
San just wanted to help me

1135
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:54,760
get even.

1136
00:40:56,590 --> 00:40:57,360
Zhenzhu.

1137
00:40:58,030 --> 00:40:59,230
San's feelings for you

1138
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,630
are obvious to us all.

1139
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:03,300
But have you thought about

1140
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:06,110
what will happen
after San finds Ke Yixiong?

1141
00:41:06,110 --> 00:41:07,000
Beat him up?

1142
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:09,030
Beat him until he's too scared
to mess with you?

1143
00:41:09,030 --> 00:41:10,150
Do you think someone like Ke Yixiong

1144
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:11,350
will really let it go?

1145
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:16,850
Zhenzhu.

1146
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:19,560
Let's report this to the police.

1147
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,960
Report it because I got beaten?

1148
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:23,670
Yes.

1149
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:25,150
If you don't report it,

1150
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:27,480
how will the police know there's a victim?

1151
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,510
It was Ke Yixiong

1152
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,510
who broke the law.

1153
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:30,920
Let's report it now.

1154
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,650
Let's kick him while he's down.

1155
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:34,710
But today,

1156
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:37,150
it was just some thugs who hit me.

1157
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:39,320
Ke Yixiong didn't show up personally.

1158
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,520
They won't catch him.

1159
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:41,890
Those thugs

1160
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:43,320
had no grudge against you.

1161
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:44,650
The police will find out

1162
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,150
why they beat you.

1163
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:48,230
Even if we can't catch Ke Yixiong,

1164
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,320
catching a few of his men

1165
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:51,380
will still make things worse for him.

1166
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:55,710
Zhenzhu.

1167
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:58,590
Do you actually want
to run an honest business,

1168
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:01,390
or do you want
to follow in Ke Yixiong's footsteps?

1169
00:42:02,970 --> 00:42:04,400
Did you lead the Bai Martial Arts School

1170
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,110
brothers

1171
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,680
to do something illegal?

1172
00:42:08,190 --> 00:42:08,840
If you did,

1173
00:42:09,190 --> 00:42:11,190
just pretend I never said anything.

1174
00:42:28,550 --> 00:42:29,080
Yixiong.

1175
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,290
How is business?

1176
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,190
Not bad. Not bad.

1177
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,520
Have an apple, Yixiong.

1178
00:42:33,030 --> 00:42:34,280
May you be prosperous.

1179
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:35,360
Take care, Yixiong.

1180
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,630
Come over if you want some, Yixiong!

1181
00:42:36,630 --> 00:42:37,550
Alright, alright!
